---
title: Mexican-Style Pork and Pineapple Rice with Charred Corn
description: This heart-warming rice dish is a feast for the eyes! Smokey Mexican spices are complemented by the sweetness of fresh pineapple and charred corn in this rendition of a dirty rice!
